    "It has also been adapted to technical text from medicine, supply chain, and finance.",
    "Technical text data from MWOs though, is quite distinctive.",
    "It is generated by a human source, so the language used by operators, technicians, etc.",
    "is not easy to understand due to the highly specific colloquialisms, technical jargon, short hand, abbreviations and the domain-specific terminology.",
